translation[5]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,Alif Laam Meem
  2,2,"Yeh Allah ki kitab hai, is mein koi shakk nahin, hidayat hai un parheizgaar logon ke liye"
  2,3,"Jo gaib par iman latey hain, namaz qayam karte hain , jo rizq humne unko diya hai usmein se kharch karte hain"
  2,4,Jo kitab tumpar nazil ki gayi hai (yani Quran) aur jo kitabein tumse pehle nazil ki gayi thi un sab par iman latey hain aur aakhirat par yaqeen rakhte hain
  2,5,Aisey log apne Rubb ki taraf se raah e raast par hain aur wahi falaah paney waley hain